# Implementation Plan - Avani Loan Agents

This plan outlines the architecture, features, and setup instructions to build the **Avani Loan Agents** platform. The system consists of a premium web portal for **Avani Loan Services**, an interactive AI Loan Advisor, an admin lead management dashboard, and multi-channel integrations (WhatsApp/Twilio, HubSpot, Google Sheets, Vapi, Zapier).

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Key Architectural and Integration Decisions**
> 1. **AI Model Provider**: The system will be built using the **Vercel AI SDK**, supporting multiple LLM providers. By default, it will support **Google Gemini** (`@ai-sdk/google`) and **OpenAI** (`@ai-sdk/openai`). You will need to provide the corresponding API keys (`GEMINI_API_KEY` or `OPENAI_API_KEY`) in your environment.
> 2. **Database Strategy**: We will use **SQLite** (via `better-sqlite3` or Prisma) as a local, zero-config database that stores leads and chat history. For Vercel production deployment, it will support switching to **PostgreSQL** (e.g., Neon or Supabase) via a simple environment variable (`DATABASE_URL`).
> 3. **WhatsApp / Twilio Integration**: The WhatsApp integration is set up via a Webhook endpoint (`/api/whatsapp`). It is designed to work with either **Twilio WhatsApp API** or the **Meta WhatsApp Cloud API**.
> 4. **CRM & Google Sheets Integration**: Leads will be synced to **HubSpot** using its Contacts API, and to **Google Sheets** via either Google Sheets API or a webhook (Zapier/Make).

